Provides: niri
Description: Scrollable-tiling Wayland compositor (Debian systemd build)
 Niri is a scrollable-tiling Wayland compositor. Windows are arranged in
 columns on an infinite strip going to the right. Every monitor has its own
 separate window strip.
 .
 This package is compiled from the latest git source with native optimizations
 for x86-64-v3 and fully integrates into the standard systemd-logind seat
 management architecture. Native Xwayland support is provided via
 xwayland-satellite starting from niri 25.08.
